{
  "id": "RAW_f8f75eb7",
  "title": "Introducing bash-tool for filesystem-based context retrieval - Vercel",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/changelog/introducing-bash-tool-for-filesystem-based-context-retrieval",
  "date": "2026-01-07 13:00:00",
  "author": "Malte Ubl, Andrew Qu",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__9eLiuW__content\">\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">We open-sourced <code>bash-tool</code>, the Bash execution engine used by <a target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/blog/we-removed-80-percent-of-our-agents-tools\" data-zone=\"same\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\" href=\"https://vercel.com/blog/we-removed-80-percent-of-our-agents-tools\">our text-to-SQL agent that we recently re-architected</a> to reduce our token usage, improve the accuracy of the agent's responses, and improve the agent's overall performance.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/bash-tool\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/bash-tool\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><code>bash-tool</code></a> gives your agent a way to find the right context by running bash-like commands over files, then returning only the results of those tool calls to the model.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Context windows can fill up quickly if you include large amounts of text into a prompt. As agents tend to do well with Unix-style workflows like <code>find</code>, <code>grep</code>, <code>jq</code>, and pipes, with <code>bash-tool </code>you can now keep large context <i>local, </i>in a filesystem, and let the agent use those commands to retrieve smaller slices of context on demand.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><code>bash-tool</code> provides <code>bash</code>, <code>readFile</code>, and <code>writeFile</code> tools for <a href=\"https://ai-sdk.dev\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://ai-sdk.dev\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">AI SDK</a> agents, working with both in-memory and sandboxed environments, and:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">runs on top of <a href=\"https://github.com/vercel-labs/just-bash\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://github.com/vercel-labs/just-bash\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><code>just-bash</code></a>, which interprets bash scripts directly in TypeScript without a shell process or arbitrary binary execution</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">you can preload that filesystem with your files at startup, so your agent can search them when needed without pasting everything into the prompt</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">it supports running in-memory or in a custom isolated VM</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper code-block-module__NOThwW__hasFileName blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__header\">\n      <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__fileName\">\n       <span class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__filenameP\">agent.ts</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__actions\">\n       <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-typescript code-block-module__NOThwW__pre blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__maxHeight\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> createBashTool </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"bash-tool\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> tools </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">createBashTool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  files</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string-property property\">\"src/index.ts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"export const hello = 'world';\"</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L7\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> agent </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token class-name\">ToolLoopAgent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> model</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> tools </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\">Using bash-tool with an in-memory filesystem</p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">If you need a real shell, a real filesystem, or custom binaries, you can run the same tool against a Sandbox-compatible API for full VM isolation.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper code-block-module__NOThwW__hasFileName blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__header\">\n      <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__fileName\">\n       <span class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__filenameP\">agent.ts</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__actions\">\n       <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-typescript code-block-module__NOThwW__pre blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__maxHeight\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> createBashTool </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"bash-tool\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> Sandbox </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"@vercel/sandbox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> sandbox </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> Sandbox</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> tools </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">createBashTool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> sandbox </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C5790de08-L7\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> agent </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token class-name\">ToolLoopAgent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> model</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> tools </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\">Using bash-tool with a Vercel sandbox</p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel 开源了 `bash-tool`，这是一个用于 AI 智能体的 Bash 执行引擎，能够高效地从文件系统中检索上下文，减少 token 使用并提升性能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel 开源了 `bash-tool`，这是一个用于 AI 智能体的 Bash 执行引擎，能够高效地从文件系统中检索上下文，减少 token 使用并提升性能。",
  "summary": "Vercel 推出了 `bash-tool`，这是一个开源的 Bash 执行引擎，旨在通过促进基于文件系统的上下文检索来增强 AI 智能体。该工具使智能体能够在本地文件上执行 Unix 风格命令（`find`、`grep`、`jq`），向 LLM 返回紧凑且相关的结果，从而节省 token 使用并提高智能体的准确性和性能。`bash-tool` 运行在 `just-bash` 之上，后者在 TypeScript 中解释 Bash 脚本而无需 shell 进程，支持内存中和沙盒环境。这使得智能体能够预加载和搜索大型文件系统，而不会阻塞上下文窗口，使其成为开发更高效和有效的基于 AI SDK 的智能体的宝贵补充，特别是在涉及大型代码库或文档的任务中。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "`bash-tool` 使 AI 智能体能够高效地从本地文件系统检索上下文。",
      "explanation": "通过允许智能体直接对文件执行类 Unix 命令（例如 `find`、`grep`），`bash-tool` 仅提取必要信息，向 LLM 提供紧凑的结果。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该工具显著减少了 token 使用，并提高了 AI 智能体的性能和准确性。",
      "explanation": "`bash-tool` 不是向 LLM 提供大量原始上下文，而是提供集中的、相关的信息片段，优化上下文窗口的使用并减少噪音。"
    },
    {
      "point": "`bash-tool` 安全且灵活地运行，避免了直接的 shell 进程。",
      "explanation": "它构建在 `just-bash` 之上，在 TypeScript 中解释 Bash 脚本，支持内存中和沙盒环境，以增强安全性和可扩展性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "我们开源了 `bash-tool`，这是我们最近重新架构的文本转 SQL 智能体所使用的 Bash 执行引擎，旨在减少我们的 token 使用，提高智能体响应的准确性，并改善智能体的整体性能。",
    "`bash-tool` 为您的智能体提供了一种通过运行类 bash 命令来查找正确上下文的方法，然后仅将这些工具调用的结果返回给模型。",
    "如果在提示中包含大量文本，上下文窗口可能会很快填满。由于智能体在处理类 Unix 工作流（如 `find`、`grep`、`jq` 和管道）时表现良好，使用 `bash-tool`，您现在可以将大型上下文*本地*保存在文件系统中，并让智能体使用这些命令按需检索较小的上下文片段。",
    "运行在 `just-bash` 之上，它直接在 TypeScript 中解释 bash 脚本，无需 shell 进程或任意二进制执行。"
  ],
